Summary: Donuts on a rope or smoke rings on a string
trends: There have been 129 other sightings in Albuquerque
There were no other sightings in Albuquerque on or around May 15th 2007
divs: Sighting DetailsI heard a small plane making a lot of noise overhead & looked up to see what kind it was. When i looked up there was a very ,very high plane, going very, very fast, leaving a very small contrail behind. the contrail looked like fat donuts on a thin rope. By the time i could get to a camera, the jet stream had distorted the contrail to the point it wasn't clear any longer. The plane must have been flying at 50,000 ft or more. as it was just a small dark dot in the sky.
